{"tid":877393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球首次！「AI畫家」創作肖像畫　佳士德拍賣1334萬元成交","createTime":"2018-10-26T10:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T10:50:06.000Z","uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2397903be84d040daa6d9b30a04dac235378134d","tid":877393,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3648/d3648537.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3648%2Fd3648537.jpg&h=37ad8af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紐約佳士德公司25日舉行「Prints &amp; Multiples」藝術拍賣會，其中一幅男性的人像畫最終以43.2萬美元（約新台幣1334萬元）的價格被賣出。不過仔細一看，畫作右下角署名似乎有些奇怪，竟然是一串複雜的數學方程式。原來，這幅畫作的畫家不是人類，而是人工智慧（AI）。<br />\n<br />\n據《紐約時報》報導，這幅畫作名為《貝拉米畫像》（Edmond de Belamy），畫中身型微胖的男子身穿一襲黑衣，臉部輪廓模糊，也沒有明確的表情，乍看之下似乎沒有甚麼特別之處，甚至連貝拉米這個人都不存在，不過它的價值在於，它是由法國藝術團隊「Obvious」設計的一套演算法所繪製而成。<br />\n<br />\n「Obvious」透過使用一種「生產式對抗網路」 （GAN）的演算法，輸入並分析1萬5000張14至20世紀的畫作，讓AI學習、掌握肖像畫繪製的模式，最後成功創作出一幅自己的作品。<br />\n<br />\n畫作下方署名「min max Ex[log(D(x))] + Ez[log(1-D(G(z)))]」就是AI完成畫作時，所套用的公式。「Obvious」團隊的負責人弗雷特（Pierre Fautrel）提到，「雖然是演算法繪製的作品，但我們在討論後，決定比照一般的畫作，將它印在畫布上，簽上數學公式，再裱入金框。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3648/d3648518.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3648%2Fd3648518.jpg&h=c07bb0db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這幅畫作被佳士德選作拍賣會上的其中一項商品時，弗雷特等人都不敢置信，不過拍賣會主辦人勞伊德（Richard Lloyd）回應，這幅肖像畫雖然已起了一番爭議，但它對藝術界而言意義重大，「我們在這250年間進行了無數藝術作品的交易，這幅畫也是如此，不過它可能會改變未來的藝術市場。人們可以透過這幅畫作，重新去探索藝術和創意的本質，畢竟每個人對藝術的定義都不同，如果人們與藝術品之間能夠產生共鳴或啟發，那麼它就是藝術的一部份。」<br />\n<br />\n佳士德原先預估《貝拉米畫像》應該最高能賣出1萬美元（約新台幣31萬元），沒想到最後這幅畫像經過了一名拍賣者的5次競價，最終竟以43.2萬美元結標，金額遠遠超過預估價。<br />\n<br />\n「Obvious」由3位巴黎藝術家勞伊德、維尼爾（Gauthier Vernier）以及凱瑟勒斯杜伯拉（Hugo Caselles-Dupra）在2017年4月共同創立，目前已透過讓人工智慧學習藝術歷史和作畫風格方式，繪製出11件藝術作品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181026/1290704.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181026%2F1290704.htm&d=pBvlUjHteML23fzRuHOJCmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6d364f6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181026/1290704.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5079f7c3e54240bba5135a23fa94cf43dd22d09e","tid":877393,"uid":36142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:22:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">新台幣</span>1334萬元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecccb95e6df8314bae6dc774c1fb9f4ff5e3f942","tid":877393,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:34:47.000Z","msg":"遲下ai柯篤屎可能都值錢"},{"pid":"c9f0b8e1c14f255ccaaf7df7978a06ab60918f4f","tid":877393,"uid":57513,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ecccb95e6df8314bae6dc774c1fb9f4ff5e3f942","tid":877393,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:34:47.000Z","msg":"遲下ai柯篤屎可能都值錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:42:51.000Z","msg":"ai識痾屎應該都幾利害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b094f1e043d031be521faf715e8449083c29d639","tid":877393,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecccb95e6df8314bae6dc774c1fb9f4ff5e3f942","tid":877393,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:34:47.000Z","msg":"遲下ai柯篤屎可能都值錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:46:42.000Z","msg":"Ai痾屎係唔係數碼暴龍嗰啲?十幾廿年前都有喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8579e67ed7f9b62129a97457d1c6d2eebd5e81d9","tid":877393,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5079f7c3e54240bba5135a23fa94cf43dd22d09e","tid":877393,"uid":36142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:22:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">新台幣</span>1334萬元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:47:10.000Z","msg":"港紙都幾百萬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAI想一炮過買香港樓都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68bf5771a23d7bfe4e8c9ef8f4357616fe191cf4","tid":877393,"uid":43009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:50:06.000Z","msg":"法國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港修art既啲science一定成pat屎"}]}